        <li>If you like <b>space battles &amp; hacking</b></li>
        <li class="rating"><span class="stars">★★★★☆</span><span class="muted">&nbsp;Popular</span></li>
        <li>space • AI • survival</li>
        <li class="one-liner">Two teens uncover secrets about an interstellar attack via data logs.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <button class="btn btn-gold">Start Reading</button>
        <button class="btn btn-hollow">Mark as Finished</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="book-section">
    <h2>About Illuminae</h2>
    <p>Found documents reveal a conspiracy of warships, corporations, and an AI losing its grip on sanity.</p>
  </div>
